{"id":2907,"date":"2020-02-11T14:56:50","date_gmt":"2020-02-11T07:56:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/?p=2907"},"modified":"2020-02-12T08:30:17","modified_gmt":"2020-02-12T01:30:17","slug":"nhung-mau-rem-cua-dep-nhat-2020","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/nhung-mau-rem-cua-dep-nhat-2020.html","title":{"rendered":"Nh\u1eefng M\u1eabu R\u00e8m C\u1eeda \u0110\u1eb9p Nh\u1ea5t 2020"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong><em>Nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y. Gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh!<br \/>\n<\/em><\/strong><strong><em>B\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ea7n l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1ec3 trang tr\u00ed cho c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh? B\u1ea1n \u0111ang ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u1eeda n\u00e0o ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi gia \u0111\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n? b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u01b0u nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? Th\u00ec \u0111\u1eebng b\u1ecf qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1eafc m\u1eafc khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m c\u1eeda c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ngay th\u00f4i<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 130%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\">1 R\u00e8m V\u1ea3i Hai L\u1edbp<br \/>\n<\/span><\/strong><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-hai-lop\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp<\/span><\/a> l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o gi\u1eefa r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u00e0 r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i voan trang tr\u00ed. V\u1eady n\u00ean, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m v\u1eeba c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ch\u1eafn s\u00e1ng v\u1eeba c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n cho c\u0103n nh\u00e0 th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o<br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2725 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pn-09-2-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1312\" height=\"985\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pn-09-2-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pn-09-2-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pn-09-2-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pn-09-2-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pn-09-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1312px) 100vw, 1312px\" title=\"\"><br \/>\nLo\u1ea1i <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-hai-lop\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp<\/span><\/a> n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t v\u1ea3i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ec3u may. V\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o b\u1edfi 2 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i, l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i m\u1ecfng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y d\u1eb7n b\u00ean trong. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i v\u1ea3i voan m\u1ecfng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 t\u00f4n l\u00ean v\u1ebb nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, b\u1ed3ng b\u1ec1nh cho b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m th\u00ec l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y b\u00ean trong c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m t\u1ea1o n\u00ean v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p ho\u00e0n m\u1ef9. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c may t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 g\u1ea5m, cotton, b\u1ed1, l\u1ee5a,&#8230; \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, ch\u1eafn s\u00e1ng, gi\u00fap c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u <img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2731 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/a2c810b339c2c09c99d3-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1319\" height=\"989\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/a2c810b339c2c09c99d3-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/a2c810b339c2c09c99d3-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/a2c810b339c2c09c99d3-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/a2c810b339c2c09c99d3.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1319px) 100vw, 1319px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>T\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5t v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y b\u00ean trong m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ki\u1ec3u may kh\u00e1c nhau. Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 ki\u1ec3u may: Ore \u0111\u1ee5c l\u1ed7, ki\u1ec3u may chi\u1ebft ly, ki\u1ec3u may \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh,&#8230; Sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p th\u00eam l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i voan b\u00ean trong sao cho h\u00e0i h\u00f2a v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t <img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2333 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-1-lop-06-3-Copy-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1332\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-1-lop-06-3-Copy-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-1-lop-06-3-Copy-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-1-lop-06-3-Copy-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-1-lop-06-3-Copy.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1332px) 100vw, 1332px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1ea3i may v\u00e0 m\u1eabu m\u00e3 c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc hoaa v\u0103n tr\u00ean b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u1eady n\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng n\u00e0o? B\u1edfi n\u1ebfu ch\u1ecdn sai, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m th\u00eam c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-1957 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/ed897653f7d8118648c9-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1328\" height=\"997\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/ed897653f7d8118648c9-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/ed897653f7d8118648c9-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/ed897653f7d8118648c9-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/ed897653f7d8118648c9-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/ed897653f7d8118648c9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1328px) 100vw, 1328px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 130%; color: #800080;\">2. R\u00e8m C\u1ea7u V\u1ed3ng<br \/>\n<\/span><\/strong>C\u00e1i t\u00ean <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-cau-vong\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng<\/span><\/a> kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa l\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eefa. C\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-cau-vong\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng<\/span><\/a> r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p cao c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf g\u1ed3m 2 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i. T\u1ea1o n\u00ean hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng b\u1eaft \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1 tinh t\u1ebf, mang \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-1969 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pk-1816-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1311\" height=\"984\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pk-1816-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pk-1816-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pk-1816-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pk-1816-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-pk-1816.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1311px) 100vw, 1311px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-cau-vong\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">M\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng<\/span><\/a> c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, d\u1ec5 v\u1ec7 sinh n\u00ean ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u1ebfn v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, nh\u1eefng qu\u00e1n cafe sang tr\u1ecdng,&#8230;<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2869 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-cv-09-3-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1315\" height=\"987\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-cv-09-3-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-cv-09-3-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-cv-09-3-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-cv-09-3-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-cv-09-3.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1315px) 100vw, 1315px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-cau-vong\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda C\u1ea7u V\u1ed3ng<\/span><\/a> c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn cao c\u1ea5p, t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng b\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u, n\u00ean c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n tham kh\u1ea3o nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00ec h\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu<a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-cau-vong\/\"><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"> r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng<\/span><\/a> b\u00ean R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-1064 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/2f6178b7dd623b3c6273-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1331\" height=\"1774\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/2f6178b7dd623b3c6273-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/2f6178b7dd623b3c6273-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/2f6178b7dd623b3c6273-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/2f6178b7dd623b3c6273-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/2f6178b7dd623b3c6273.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1331px) 100vw, 1331px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 130%; color: #800080;\">3. R\u00e8m Roman<br \/>\n<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-roman\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">R\u00e8m roman<\/span><\/a> hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 m\u00e0n roman thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo d\u1ea1ng r\u00e8m x\u1ebfp l\u1edbp \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng. V\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng s\u1eeda d\u1ee5ng c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng h\u1eefu \u00edch \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2916 aligncenter\" style=\"font-size: 14.4px;\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-ngu-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1320\" height=\"1320\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-ngu-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-ngu-510x510.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-ngu-280x280.jpg 280w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-ngu-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-ngu-800x800.jpg 800w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-ngu-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-ngu.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1320px) 100vw, 1320px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-roman\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">M\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda roman \u0111\u1eb9p<\/span><\/a> c\u00f3 m\u1eabu m\u00e3, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng phong ph\u00fa. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ecdn m\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda roman l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0u s\u1eafc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00f2n r\u00e8m th\u00ec h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean b\u00ean R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh lo. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1eabu r\u00e8m Roman c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, th\u1eadm tr\u00ed l\u00e0 c\u00e1c qu\u00e1n cafe, hay c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng \u0103n u\u1ed1ng v\u00ec nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t cao<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2918 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-khach-600x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1313\" height=\"876\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-khach-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-khach-510x340.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-khach-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-khach-1199x800.jpg 1199w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-roman-cho-phong-khach.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1313px) 100vw, 1313px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 130%; color: #800080;\">4. R\u00e8m g\u1ed7<br \/>\n<\/span><\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-sao-go\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">R\u00e