 nh\u00f4m<\/a>,<\/span> &#8230; \u0111ang d\u1ea7n thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-sao-go\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">r\u00e8m g\u1ed7<\/span><\/a> m\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u00e0nh r\u00e8m, b\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 m\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u00f2n \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c g\u1ea7n g\u0169i, \u1ea5m \u00e1p v\u00e0 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi con ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-1293 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/fb7ed21ee02f06715f3e-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1299\" height=\"975\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/fb7ed21ee02f06715f3e-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/fb7ed21ee02f06715f3e-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/fb7ed21ee02f06715f3e-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/fb7ed21ee02f06715f3e-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/fb7ed21ee02f06715f3e.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1299px) 100vw, 1299px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 130%;\">5. R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n<br \/>\n<\/span><\/strong><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-cuon\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">M\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda cu\u1ed1n<\/span><\/a> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m. C\u00f3 c\u1ea7u t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00ean r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, V\u1edbi r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o l\u00ean cao h\u1ebft \u01